#~ msgid ""
#~ "Autocorrection is &kpresenter;'s ability to correct common typing errors "
#~ "or expand abbreviations independently of the spell checking function. "
#~ "There are several common typing errors entered for you by default such as "
#~ "replacing <userinput>teh</userinput> with <userinput>the</userinput> and "
#~ "you can add as many more as you like."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "La correzione automatica è la capacità di &kpresenter; di correggere gli "
#~ "errori di battitura comuni o espandere le abbreviazioni indipendentemente "
